text: Rodrigo Diego Lopez (born 2 December 1996) is a Mexican diver. He competed in the men's three metre springboard event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male divers Category:Olympic divers of Mexico Category:Divers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Divers at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics
